      "text": "# The Three-Body Problem\n\nThe Three-Body Problem is a science fiction novel written by Chinese author Liu Cixin, the first book in the \"Remembrance of Earth's Past\" trilogy.\n\n## Synopsis\n\nDuring the Cultural Revolution, astrophysicist Ye Wenjie is brought to a secret military project called \"Red Coast\" after surviving numerous hardships. Using the sun as an antenna, Ye Wenjie sends Earth's first signal into the universe, making a breakthrough in the search for extraterrestrial civilization.\n\n## Product Information\n\n- **Title**: The Three-Body Problem\n- **Author**: Liu Cixin\n- **Genre**: Science Fiction\n- **Price**: 50 WOW\n\n![Book Cover](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532012197267-da84d127e765?w=800)\n\n![Space Scene](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1462331940025-496dfbfc7564?w=800)",
